{"tid":1747203,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[白票/廢票/唔投]求下你地用手上嘅一票替已犧牲/未成年嘅手足投票","createTime":"2019-11-23T06:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T15:18:01.000Z","uid":157597,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"04fceeaa3df6736072979dc64f95913b94c7e7af","tid":1747203,"uid":157597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:21:13.000Z","msg":"已經走左嘅手足、未成年嘅學生、被黑警拉左打到昏迷等等，好想投票嘅人都無得投，佢地為左呢場運動犧牲/付出左好多好多，一張選票對佢地黎講已經係非常遙遠。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">既然你放棄你手上嘅選票嘅話，我而家跪求你地將選票送俾佢地，諗下梁烈士、陳彥霖同學、周同學、被消失被自殺嘅人等等，諗下佢地會點投票，幫佢地投票好嗎？求下你地&hellip;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我見呢兩日有人講唔好投俾泛民，我唔知佢地係咩野人，就算俾人話我係泛民打手都唔介意，相比起手足所付出嘅根本不值一提&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我講野唔叻但都希望大家幫下手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後都係果句求下你地幫手足投票</span></span><br />\n<br />\n612 721 831 101 1111 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/caS2LGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcaS2LGE.jpg&h=128c22b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cq3xotm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCq3xotm.jpg&h=ee1fecff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V7suqGH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV7suqGH.jpg&h=75dc2b01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TM1ySmA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTM1ySmA.jpg&h=81638e5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BdoYi1B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdoYi1B.jpg&h=1d16192f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fcRfmeX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfcRfmeX.jpg&h=4e97fd67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ER8Yi1D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FER8Yi1D.jpg&h=51cb3b